Package assegnamento3.src

Class Wine

java.lang.Object
assegnamento3.src.Wine
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Wine
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
The Wine class defines the different kinds of wines.

Wines are defined by the name, the producer, the year of production, some technical notes and the grape type.

The number specifies how much bottles of wine are available.

Each wine is identified by a unique id.
